00 UTC using the premium index between perpetual and spot prices. Portfolio margin mode allows cross-margining with other positions, reducing capital requirements for delta-neutral arbitrage strategies. The exchange's multi-asset margin system enables efficient capital utilization across NEAR and other Layer-1 tokens simultaneously."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
